<h2>ternvis: Visualisation, Verification and Calibration of Ternary
Probabilistic Forecasts</h2>
<p>A suite of functions for visualising ternary probabilistic forecasts, as discussed in the paper by Jupp (2012) &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1098%2Frsta.2011.0350">doi:10.1098/rsta.2011.0350</a>&gt;.</p>
